<HL>
   Senate Clears
   Ryan to Head
   S&amp;L Regulation
   ---
   Vote Nullifies Court Ruling
   That Derailed Overhaul;
   Wide Margin Surprising
   ----
   By Paulette Thomas
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
04/05/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE A3
</SO>
<IN>
SAVINGS AND LOANS, THRIFTS, CREDIT UNIONS (SAL)
TENDER OFFERS, MERGERS, ACQUISITIONS (TNM)
</IN>
